      "description": "This F87 BMW M2 Competition represents a pinnacle of modern chassis engineering, powered by the S55 3.0L biturbo inline-six featuring a closed-deck design for maximum thermal efficiency and boost stability. The drivetrain utilizes an Active M Differential and an M-DCT gearbox for instantaneous torque distribution across the rear axle. This vehicle is in collector-grade condition, boasting a CFRP high-precision strut brace for enhanced front-end turn-in and factory-spec 19-inch 788M forged wheels. Mechanically flawless with zero modifications, it offers a visceral driving experience with high-speed lateral stability and precise steering feedback.",
